casebody.data:
Matthew J. MEDLIN
v.
Donnie HARRISON No. 351P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 19, 2017. Matthew J. Medlin, for Medlin, Matthew J. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Harrison, Donnie (Sheriff of Wake)

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 18th of October 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 19th of October 2017."
